---
// MyProjects component
---

<!-- Projects -->
<section id="projects" class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 sm:text-4xl">
      Mis Proyectos
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-center text-slate-600">
      Algunos de los trabajos en los que he estado trabajando
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

      <!-- CEDISJ -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-300">CEDISJ</h3>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-green-600 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white shrink-0">Completado</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Repositorio para gestión documental de proyectos, monografías, prácticas, informes y eventos en tiempo real para las carreras de Sociología, Psicología y Derecho en la Universidad Popular del Cesar.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">React</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">Node.js</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">Firebase</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Ver código de CEDISJ" class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            Ver código
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Web de CEDISJ" class="rounded-full border border-indigo-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-indigo-50">
            Web
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- GNEIS -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors duration-300">GNEIS</h3>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-green-600 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white shrink-0">Completado</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Plataforma web para la gestión integral del Hotel Neruda Mar: reservas, habitaciones, check-in / check-out, información física y facturación.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">React</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">Node.js</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">SQL Server</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">Tailwind CSS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Ver código de GNEIS" class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            Ver código
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Web de GNEIS" class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-emerald-50">
            Web
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MR. CHOFER -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors duration-300">Mr. Chofer</h3>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-green-600 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white shrink-0">Completado</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Aplicación móvil para solicitar motocicletas en encargos y traslados, con mapas interactivos, rutas en tiempo real y roles diferenciados: Conductor, Usuario y Administrador.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-orange-700">React Native</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-orange-700">Node.js</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-orange-700">Maps API</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-orange-700">Socket.io</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Ver código de Mr. Chofer" class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            Ver código
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Web de Mr. Chofer" class="rounded-full border border-orange-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-orange-50">
            Web
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- KENWA -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors duration-300">KENWA</h3>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-green-600 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white shrink-0">Completado</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Web y app móvil para la gestión de tiempos de descanso y niveles de estrés laboral, con indicadores, cronómetros y gráficas interactivas para promover un ambiente de trabajo saludable.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700">React</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700">React Native</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700">Chart.js</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-purple-700">Supabase</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="https://github.com/Gsus07/kenwa-pages" aria-label="Ver código de KENWA" class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            Ver código
          </a>
          <a href="https://kenwa.pages.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Web de KENWA" class="rounded-full border border-purple-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-purple-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-purple-50">
            Web
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- VALIDADOR CUVAPP -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl group sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors duration-300">Validador CUVAPP</h3>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-indigo-500 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white shrink-0">En desarrollo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Plataforma web de uso institucional para la validación de medicamentos ante el INVIMA, con visualización de estados actualizados por producto.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">React</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">Python</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">SQL Server</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-700">Pandas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Ver código de Validador CUVAPP" class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            Ver código
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Web de Validador CUVAPP" class="rounded-full border border-sky-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-sky-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-sky-50">
            Web
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</section>